            </div>
            <p class="text-sm mt-4">
                Pubs featured on this website have been independently added and updated by thousands of CAMRA volunteers and includes over 96% of Britain's cask ale pubs. Enjoy!
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-4">
                <strong>31,581</strong> cask ale venues currently listed, <strong>30,392</strong> with complete details.
            </p>
        </div>
